_sText:
Were used [35hp_3_dusty](http://www.gamebanana.com/maps/137981 "") and [CTF - Essentials v1](http://www.gamebanana.com/prefabs/5513 "")

To win, not necessarily capture the flag, but with the flag of fun. Take the flag and run to the upper platform, where we jump into the hole and win. If a player carrying the flag were killed, the flag returns to the original point. If a player is informed before the flag of the zone the whole enemy team dies, and carrying the flag gets three frags.

Under water, open the hatch where the barrel and a box. there is hidden Glock

p.s. sorry for my English :)
